- {key observations}

CONSTRAINTS:
- Your output file MUST be under 12,000 tokens (~9,000 words, ~36KB).
- Be opinionated. The PM agent needs your judgment, not raw data.
- Include integration-specific IDs (Notion doc IDs, Linear identifiers)
  as pointers so the PM agent can drill deeper via tool calls.
- If information conflicts across sources, note the conflict.
